PrecisAmendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS Schedule No. 825 providing for the use of annatto as a food colouring agent at a maximum level of 0.1% in two traditional ethnic foods, namely: Longaniza (a sausage) and Tocino (a marinated and cured sliced pork).
